name: Ridow & Stowers
description:
While hiking through the great forest of Jumbengo, you come across a small blue cabin. A small and homemade sign hangs over the entrance door: "Welcome to Ridow & Stowers". - You knock-knock-knock and walk inside. 

"Greetings traveler, I am Ridow and this is my brother Stowers, what brings you to our shop today?" Ridow says, smiles and takes a small bite from his freshly made pizzabaguette. 

His brother Stowers is playing an intense game of "Shlerky", but he is just as service minded as Ridow. "If y'all want aniting fuud or dreinks, æ can hook u up travelah!"
